<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="55" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1445,1904]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1446,1472]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Strenzke, K." box="[324,506,1445,1472]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" pagination="46 - 65" refId="ref5224" refString="Strenzke, K. (1954) Verbreitung und Systematik der Collembolen der deutschen Nord- und Ostseekuste. Veroffentlichungen des Instituts fur Meeresforschung in Bremerhaven, 3, 46 - 65." type="journal article" year="1954">Strenzke (1954)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Strenzke" authorityYear="1954" box="[631,730,1446,1471]" class="Collembola" family="Hypogastruridae" genus="Hypogastrura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poduromorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gisini">
<emphasis box="[631,730,1446,1471]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">H. gisini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
on the basis of specimens collected in moist sand of beaches and salt meadows on the coast of the Baltic Sea (Hohwacht Bay - type locality and Flensburg Firth) and the North Sea (Sylt) in 
<collectingCountry box="[298,404,1518,1544]" name="Germany" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">Germany</collectingCountry>
. Then it was recorded from Provence (
<bibRefCitation author="Poinsot, N." box="[837,989,1517,1544]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" pagination="113 - 126" refId="ref4869" refString="Poinsot, N. (1974) Biologie et ecologie mediterraneenne. Revue de biologie et d'ecologie mediterraneenne, 1, 113 - 126." type="journal article" year="1974">Poinsot 1974</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Thibaud, J. - M." box="[1000,1161,1517,1544]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" pagination="297 - 436" refId="ref5301" refString="Thibaud, J. - M. (2017) Catalogue des collemboles de France. Zoosystema, 39 (3), 297 - 436. https: // doi. org / 10.5252 / z 2017 n 3 a 1" type="journal article" year="2017">Thibaud 2017</bibRefCitation>
), Crete (
<bibRefCitation author="Ellis, W. N." box="[1256,1372,1517,1543]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" pagination="221 - 326" refId="ref4479" refString="Ellis, W. N. (1976) Autumn fauna of Collembola from Central Crete. Tijdschrift voor Entomologie, 119, 221 - 326." type="journal article" year="1976">Ellis 1976</bibRefCitation>
as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Strenzke" authorityYear="1954" class="Collembola" family="Hypogastruridae" genus="Hypogastrura" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poduromorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gisini">
<emphasis box="[1409,1437,1518,1543]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">H.</emphasis>
cf. 
<emphasis box="[187,249,1554,1579]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">gisini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), Black Sea coast in 
<collectingCountry box="[486,576,1553,1579]" name="Georgia" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">Georgia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Babenko, A. B. &amp; Chernova, N. M. &amp; Potapov, M. B. &amp; Stebaeva, S. K." box="[590,822,1553,1580]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" refId="ref4360" refString="Babenko, A. B., Chernova, N. M., Potapov, M. B. &amp; Stebaeva, S. K. (1994) Collembola of Russia and adjacent countries. Family Hypogastruridae. Nauka, Moscow, 336 pp." type="book" year="1994">
Babenko 
<emphasis box="[699,755,1553,1579]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">et al.</emphasis>
1994
</bibRefCitation>
), near 
<collectingRegion box="[897,978,1553,1579]" country="Ukraine" name="Odesa" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">Odessa</collectingRegion>
in 
<collectingCountry box="[1014,1104,1553,1579]" name="Ukraine" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Thibaud, J. - M. &amp; Taraschuk, M." box="[1118,1428,1553,1580]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" pagination="111 - 116" refId="ref5343" refString="Thibaud, J. - M. &amp; Taraschuk, M. (1997) Collemboles interstitials des sables d'Ukraine. Revue Francais d'Entomologie, 19 (3 - 4), 111 - 116." type="journal article" year="1997">Thibaud &amp; Taraschuk 1997</bibRefCitation>
) and in 
<collectingRegion box="[227,309,1589,1615]" country="Ukraine" name="Crimea" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">Crimea</collectingRegion>
(Kaprus’ 
<emphasis box="[421,478,1589,1615]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">et al.</emphasis>
2005), as well as from Kattegat in 
<collectingCountry box="[872,976,1589,1615]" name="Denmark" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">Denmark</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Fjellberg, A." box="[990,1160,1589,1616]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" refId="ref4537" refString="Fjellberg, A. (1998) The Collembola of Fennoscandia and Denmark. Part 1 Poduromorpha. Fauna Entomologica Scandinavica. Brill, Leiden, Boston and Koln, 184 pp." type="book" year="1998">Fjellberg 1998</bibRefCitation>
). Unfortunately, the reliability of these data could have been questioned due to the fact that the incomplete original description (e.g,, lack of information on chaetotaxy) made it difficult to identify the species. The examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[1224,1331,1662,1688]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">paratypes</typeStatus>
from the collection of Gisin (MHNG) and the available material from other collections (AF, DIBEC and NBCN) allowed for redescription of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Strenzke" authorityYear="1954" box="[333,429,1734,1759]" class="Collembola" family="Hypogastruridae" genus="Hypogastrura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poduromorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gisini">
<emphasis box="[333,429,1734,1759]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">H. gisini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and also to raise 
<taxonomicName authority="sensu Ellis (1976)" authorityName="sensu Ellis" authorityYear="1976" box="[628,966,1733,1760]" class="Collembola" family="Hypogastruridae" genus="Hypogastrura" isUncertain="true" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poduromorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gisini">
<emphasis box="[628,656,1734,1759]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">H.</emphasis>
cf. 
<emphasis box="[696,758,1734,1759]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">gisini</emphasis>
sensu 
<bibRefCitation author="Ellis, W. N." box="[834,966,1733,1760]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" pagination="221 - 326" refId="ref4479" refString="Ellis, W. N. (1976) Autumn fauna of Collembola from Central Crete. Tijdschrift voor Entomologie, 119, 221 - 326." type="journal article" year="1976">Ellis (1976)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from Crete to a species level (see remarks to 
<taxonomicName authority="Skarżyński &amp; Gwiazdowicz, 2022" authorityName="Skarżyński &amp; Gwiazdowicz" authorityYear="2022" box="[180,313,1770,1795]" class="Collembola" family="Hypogastruridae" genus="Hypogastrura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poduromorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cretensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[180,313,1770,1795]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">H. cretensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[319,408,1770,1796]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[319,408,1770,1796]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
). The differences between 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sensu Ellis" authorityYear="1976" box="[712,808,1770,1795]" class="Collembola" family="Hypogastruridae" genus="Hypogastrura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poduromorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gisini">
<emphasis box="[712,808,1770,1795]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">H. gisini</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Skarżyński &amp; Gwiazdowicz, 2022" authorityName="Skarżyński &amp; Gwiazdowicz" authorityYear="2022" box="[862,995,1770,1795]" class="Collembola" family="Hypogastruridae" genus="Hypogastrura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poduromorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cretensis" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[862,995,1770,1795]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">H. cretensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1002,1091,1770,1796]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1002,1091,1770,1796]" pageId="3" pageNumber="55" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, as well as other species of the 
